In session PSI processing:

- input thread sees an PAT TP
  - invoke_pat_snoop() -> parse_pat_tp()
    - snoop_section(): search for complete PSI section in the TP payload
                       copy snooped segment into snoop buffer
    - snoop_pat_section(): return 1 only if new PAT section is snooped
    - upate_pat()
      - clean up all program in the in session if needed
      - clean PID table
      - allocate in_prog
      - set up PAT and PMT PIDs in PID table

- input thread sees an PMT TP
  - invoke_pmt_snoop() -> parse_pmt_tp()
    - snoop_section()
    - snoop_pmt_section(): return 1 only if new PMT section is snooped
    - pmt_pid_table_remove(): clean up pid table if needed
    - parse_pmt()
    - pmt_pid_table_add()


---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Out session configuration:

- process_video_out_session_config()
  - provision_qam_flow()
  - out_session_init()
    - set up out session according to out config and in session
    - set up pid table
    - out_session_psi_init()
      - out_session_update_pat(): update QAM's PAT
        - clean up program in out_session
        - clean up PID table
        - check for PMT PID / program number collision
        - allocate out_prog
        - add PMT PID in PID table
      - regenerate_pmt(): for remap sesion only
        - clean up PMT pid/program number from pid table/usage map
        - free PMT sections and carousel buffers
        - copy input PMT section to output PMT section
        - parse_pmt(): to set up pointers
        - pmt_modify(): for prog_num and pid remap
        - psi_session_packetize(): to generate PMT carousel
        - Add ES pids to PID table
        - crsl_insert_schedule(): send 1st PMT carousel right away
    - regenerate_pat()
      - qam_collect_prog_into
        - collect all prog_num/pmt_pid from qam's session/program list
      - qam_build_pat
        - construct PAT sections and PAT carousel
        - parse_pat(): to set up pointers

---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Out session PSI processing:

Note: for new PAT/PMT TP, the new_pai_flag in tp_info will be set.

- out thread sees a tpinfo for PAT TP:
  - out_session_update_pat()
  - regenerate_pat()


- out thread sees a tpinfo for PMT TP:
  - regenerate_pmt()


